BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Contact – Iwona Boyle\, iwona3@msn.com<mailto:iwona3@msn.com>
 \nFrom: jleiz@aol.com<mailto:jleiz@aol.com> <jleiz@aol.com<mailto:jleiz@ao
 l.com>>\nDate: Sunday\, September 29\, 2024 at 7:53 PM\nTo: Solomon\, Ian 
 H. (ihs8m) <ihs8m@virginia.edu<mailto:ihs8m@virginia.edu>>\nCc: Larry Morr
 is <larry.morris@prgx.com<mailto:larry.morris@prgx.com>>\, Henry\, Andrea 
 Marie (amh4tb) <amh4tb@virginia.edu<mailto:amh4tb@virginia.edu>>\, kkt8c@v
 irginia.ed<mailto:kkt8c@virginia.ed> <kkt8c@virginia.ed<mailto:kkt8c@virgi
 nia.ed>>\nSubject: Introduction to 2024-2025 UVA Swim & Dive team.\nDear D
 ean Solomon\,\n\nI hope this message finds you and your family and Dante a
 ll doing well and enjoying the wonderful fall season.\n\nLast year's gradu
 ating swimmers & divers and their families so much enjoyed the Thursday ev
 ening dinner party that you graciously lent your garden for last May that 
 this year's group asked me if they might possibly reprise that fantastic e
 vent ahead of this coming spring's Final exercises.\n\nWith Amanda having 
 now graduated\, I have passed the torch to Larry Morris\, father of fourth
  year swimmer Kate Morris.  Please let this serve as an introduction to La
 rry and the 2024-2025 UVA Swim & Dive team.\n\nThank you very much for any
  suggestions you might have.\n\nBest regards and go Hoos\,\n\nJon Leizman\
 n216-479-9063\n\n
