DESCRIPTION:Harwood\, Charlotte (exa8bu) <exa8bu@virginia.edu>\; Dickerson\
 , Kailyn Lanae (abr2sj) <abr2sj@virginia.edu>\; Foliaco\, Kayla Christina 
 (kcf8qh) <kcf8qh@virginia.edu>\n\nGood Morning Ms. Thurston\,\n\nI hope yo
 u are doing well. I met with Dean Solomon and the Faculty Executive Commit
 tee yesterday\, and he reiterated that he would love to host social events
  at his Pavilion.\n\nWe were wondering if he would be available for the fo
 llowing events:\n\n  *   Wednesday\, October 1\, 6-8pm for “Sunset & S
 ’mores”\n  *   Tuesday\, October 28\, 7-9pm for “Karaoke with the De
 an”\n\nI’ve CC’ed our Social Chair\, Charlotte Harwood\, and VP Kail
 yn Dickerson on this email as well since they will be helping plan the eve
 nts.\n\nThanks!\n\nBest\,\nFaith Windbigler\nBatten Undergraduate Council 
 President\n--\nFaith Windbigler\nUniversity of Virginia\nB.A. Public Polic
 y & Leadership | Class of 2026\n(720) 364-2837\nzyx5rs@virginia.edu<mailto
 :zyx5rs@virginia.edu>\n\n\n\n\n
