BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:From: Krim\, Mikaela <KrimM25@darden.virginia.edu<mailto:KrimM2
 5@darden.virginia.edu>>\nSent: Tuesday\, October 28\, 2025 11:50:02 AM\nTo
 : Solomon\, Ian H. (ihs8m) <ihs8m@virginia.edu<mailto:ihs8m@virginia.edu>>
 \nSubject: Range Event Inquiry\n\nHi Dean Solomon\,\n\nI am the social cha
 ir for the Range\; we’ve spoken at a couple events. Last time we connect
 ed\, I mentioned how much Rangers enjoyed your 2023 whiskey-tasting event 
 outside Pav X (I think it’s Pav X!).\n\nI wanted to reach out to see if 
 you’d be interested in hosting another similar event for this year’s R
 angers. We have a fairly light schedule for the rest of the semester\, and
  could dip from our budget to provide snacks/ food.\n\nDo you have any ava
 ilability? Would you be interested in doing an event with us?\n\nThank you
  so much!\n\nMikaela Krim\nPhD Candidate\, Strategy\, Ethics\, and Entrepr
 eneurship\n[Receiver with solid fill](484) 788 2528\n[Cursor with solid fi
 ll]linkedin.com\\in\\mikaelakrim<https://www.linkedin.com/in/mikaelakrim/>
 \n[Envelope with solid fill]krimm25@darden.virginia.edu<mailto:krimm25@dar
 den.virginia.edu>\n[University of Virginia Darden School of Business\, ema
 il logo]\n\n\n\n
